* A starship's paralight system is a combination of mechanical and opto-
electronic subsystems found in a @{"hyperdrive" link SWG:Data/hyperdri.GDE/MAIN}. It is responsible for
translating a pilot's manual commands into a set of corresponding reactions
within the hyperdrive power plants.

